       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6KYC02.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-CUSTOMER.
           05  WS-CUSTOMER-ID        PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05  WS-SYNC-STATE         PIC X(8) VALUE SPACES.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-CUSTOMER-ID
           PERFORM 2100-VALIDATE-FOR-SYNC
           DISPLAY WS-SYNC-STATE
           STOP RUN.
       2100-VALIDATE-FOR-SYNC.
           IF WS-CUSTOMER-ID NOT = SPACES
              MOVE 'READY' TO WS-SYNC-STATE
           ELSE
              MOVE 'REJECTED' TO WS-SYNC-STATE
           END-IF.
